    "The Appendix describes the PIM virtio specification we plan to discuss with the OASIS VIRTIO Technical Committee.",
    "This section introduces UPMEM PIM (UPMEM for short).",
    "We use the latter for three main reasons.",
    "(1) UPMEM is the most recent PIM technology that can be employed on off-the-shelf machines.",
    "Other commercial PIM devices [3,35] need special memory technologies."
